Semantic Similarities

Shows the semantic similarities between documents based on where the terms appear in the text.

obSimDocs <- textstat_simil(onBeingdfm, selection = NULL, margin = c("documents") ,method = "correlation", upper = FALSE, diag = FALSE)

obSimDocs <- as.matrix(obSimDocs)

library(gplots)
## 
## Attaching package: 'gplots'
## The following object is masked from 'package:stats':
## 
##     lowess
heatmap.2(obSimDocs[1:25,1:25], Rowv=NA, Colv=NA,  margins=c(5,10), dendrogram = "none")
